model.hed: The Best New Menswear to Buy Right Now
model.dek: Our favorite brand spanking-new gear from around the web this week

items.title: Coach Camo Coat
items.caption:
Coach’s fall outwear is just so damn good—and it's just their first season doing menswear ever. This camo parka is as practical as it is stylish. 

*$895, available at [Mr Porter.com](http://www.mrporter.com/en-us/mens/coach/shearling-trimmed-camouflage-print-canvas-coat/599954)*

items.title: BALLY JC MEN'S SUEDE ANKLE BOOT IN GREY
items.caption:
Because you already own a brown and black boot, why not step up your game with a hiking-ready one in gray suede?

*695, available at [bally.com](http://www.bally.com/en_us/shop-man/shoes/boots/jc-hiker-mens-suede-ankle-boot-in-grey-6198944.html#start=1)*

items.title: John Elliott + Co. Baseline Sweatpants
items.caption:
The sweat pant that works for the entire weekend. 

*$228, available at [needsuply.com](http://needsupply.com/mens/baseline-sweats-in-dark-grey.html)*

items.title: Z Zegna Techmerino Light Sneaker
items.caption:
A running shoe that performs just as well as it looks. 

$395, available at [store.zegna.com](http://store.zegna.com/us/men/sneakers_cod44913138ho.html)*

items.title: Baxter of California Night Cream
items.caption:
That one product that will make you look as if you had a full night of sleep—even if you didn't. 

*$24, available at [baxterofcalofornia.com](http://www.baxterofcalifornia.com/C-ENC.html?cgid=skincare-face#start=6&cgid=skincare-face)*

items.title: GIVENCHY DUFFLE COAT
items.caption:
It’s the anti-prep school duffle coat. 

*$2,700, available at [Mr Porter.com](http://www.mrporter.com/en-us/mens/givenchy/leather-trimmed-wool-duffle-coat/563761)*

items.title: Grayers Double Cloth Henley
items.caption:
A few heavier henleys will give you infinite layering options when it starts to really get cold. 

*$75, available at [grayers.com](http://www.grayers.com/shop/new-arrivals/byron-double-cloth-henley-heather-white-4601/)*

items.title: Champion Logo Hoodie
items.caption:
Yeah yeah, it’s just a hoodie, but it’s a classic. And you don’t mess with a classic.
$60, available at [urbanoutfitters.com](http://www.urbanoutfitters.com/urban/catalog/productdetail.jsp?id=36005759&category=M_NEWARRIVALS_CLOTHING&color=032)

You need some blue suede kicks. These sneakers are a good option if snazzy hard-bottoms aren’t for you. 

*$120, available at [jcrew.com](https://www.jcrew.com/mens_category/shoes/sneakers/PRD~E1371/E1371.jsp?color_name=blue%20ribbon&styles=E1371-EF1597)*

items.title: J.Crew Turtleneck Sweater
items.caption:
You’re not gonna find a more multi-tasking sweater than the turtleneck this season. Prepare to suit up with it, throw it on with your jeans, and even your sweats for those early morning coffee runs.
*$89.50, available at [jcrew.com](https://www.jcrew.com/mens_feature/NewArrivals/sweaters/PRDOVR~24418/24418.jsp)

items.title: Mondaine Watch
items.caption:
Brown leather watches with minimal faces were made for the fall. The final touch to that tried and true jeans, T-shirt, and army jacket look.
*$395, available at [Mr Porter](http://www.mrporter.com/en-us/mens/mondaine/helvetica-no1-light-stainless-steel-and-leather-watch/662849)

items.title: NEEDLES REBUILD FIREMAN’S JACKET
items.caption:
The Frankenstein of waxed jackets. This is how you stand out amongst a sea of Barbour. 

*$589, available at [endclothing.com](http://www.endclothing.com/us/latest-products/new-this-week/needles-rebuild-fireman-jacket-ey-250-ol.html)*

items.title: Maison Margiela Cashmere Overcoat
items.caption:
With peak lapels that sharp, and cashmere that soft, you won’t need much else for the fall. (Probably won’t be able to afford anything else anyway.)
*$7,255, available at [barneys.com](http://www.barneys.com/maison-margiela-cashmere-overcoat-504151410.html#prefn1=newArrival&prefv1=New+Arrivals&start=44)

items.title: VISVIM FBT ELK WHITE
items.caption:
The shoe that made Visvim a household name just got a wintry-upgrade. Be precious with them if you’d like, but know these are designed to get better the more you beat ‘em up. 

*$720, available at [unionlosangeles.com](http://store.unionlosangeles.com/products/fbt-elk-1?variant=5794838277)*

items.title: Dehen x Jack Spade Jacket
items.caption:
The classic, old school varsity jacket with a little something extra. We’re game.
*$598, available at [jackspade.com](http://www.jackspade.com/dehen-x-jack-spade-r1-jacket/JSM00615.html?cgid=new-arrivals&dwvar_JSM00615_color=400#start=36&cgid=new-arrivals)
